Copy
Edit
### A Pluto.jl notebook ###
begin
	using PlutoUI, Plots
end

@bind n Slider(1:100)

plot(1:n, sqrt.(1:n))
This will display a slider, and the plot will update instantly as you move it. No "Run cell" needed.

